{"tid":1805801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有人醒目玩偷襲，成日亂屈人係五毛既連登黑警忽然好緊張！","createTime":"2019-12-31T22:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T09:38:00.000Z","uid":241151,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"23b711698157f595956c473aad21f22414f121c8","tid":1805801,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T22:50:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">班泛民左膠一定會聯絡黑警諗破解方法喇</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328f79e0aae64c031fee4a7e8aef45eeaa4e0ef1","tid":1805801,"uid":198590,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T22:50:59.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#241151 - 瀧野由美仔</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請大家保持批判性思考，善用不推文回覆，該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>人地學生就打生打死，鄺神都好自得其樂 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YW4Wctv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYW4Wctv.jpg&h=1310c14d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉&hellip;&hellip;唔好問我點解香港抗爭咁多年都係咁失敗，香港人情況仲越來越差<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fhaha.gif&h=20aa0304&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fzzz.gif&h=b6af20bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fno.gif&h=29da48de&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1714163/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1714163/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>想知乜嘢叫流水式...集會?流水就不可能集合，集合可能是在新屋嶺... - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>想知乜嘢叫流水式...集會?<br />\n流水就不可能集合，集合可能是在新屋嶺...<br />\n會唔會太過 creative, creative 到亂Q咁嚟。<br />\n定你哋較為喜愛嗌D無意思的口號，做無意義的事，好似時代革命，摺紙咁。</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1696584/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1696584/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>改口號啦！[香港人！送頭！] - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>香港人！送頭！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fzzz.gif&h=b6af20bd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1696549/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1696549/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>點呀？之前係咪話過要追究返邊d人，邊d網，邊d團體同傳媒吹市去送頭既？ - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2b0VZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT2b0VZQ.jpg&h=2ac5df0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來係連登x蘋果吹雞<br />\n難怪有哂地點時間表<br />\n鑊鑊都港島，鑊鑊都推人去死<br />\n流人哋嘅血成就自己得票當選！<br />\n泛民蘋果全部都要仆街冚家鏟！<br />\n<br />\n好彩我一早就同班泛民左膠割晒蓆姐，分化實在好！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fsmile.gif&h=0b593ebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n快d回&quot;拉，不分化，不推文回覆啦&quot;<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fzzz.gif&h=b6af20bd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1691882/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1691882/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>香港既和理非從來唔保護勇武，甚至會阻止勇武制服勇武出賣勇武，所以和理非實則係港奸 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>泛民港奸！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F